{"tid":1593261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"針對警察係無用","createTime":"2019-09-25T03:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T13:48:45.000Z","uid":16102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5cffa157de016ae2bd5f5276f1b3ef9f938d98","tid":1593261,"uid":16102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"大家有無諗過不斷針對警黑，圍警署係會令運動失焦。<br />\n<br />\n唔好妄想政府會清算黑警，因為呢個政權就係得返黑警保護佢地。有溺水過都知係會攬住會令你浮既野，現今既港共就係溺水就死既人。<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既就係，針對返港共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有真正高度自治，先可以清算黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再圍繞黑警問題，主線係清算港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港， 時代革命"},{"pid":"55ceff5c07e6aacb4a8334c13dad3a51b5212ab0","tid":1593261,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"9cf3b3bf691a08353b64380fbe7c03b02e76c115","tid":1593261,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"中共同港共係主要<br />\n佢哋係次要， 仲要共產黨鍾意就叫佢哋做condom<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似